jltl2ba

Class LTLFragments

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2ba.LTLFragments

  • public class LTLFragments
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper to determine syntactic fragments of LTL formulas.
    Each object stores information about membership in the "safety", "guarantee/co-safety", "obligation", "recurrence" and "persistence" fragments of LTL.
